title: FM08 Moskollo Database Updated to 24/6/08
description:
My own Player Database for FM08. It&#039;s updated to include Scolari at Chelsea and even has Nasri&#039;s move to boring Francais Arsenal(will the last English player turn out the light when he&#039;s gone, you really helped us in Euro 08 by the way). 

It should be quicker to download than my other files, but though I have done as many transfers as I can, I am not the Rothmans Football Yearbook 2008!

If you like this please check out my other downloads for player pictures and background screens for FM08.

The original folder was taken from the 8.02 update and I have changed and amended since the January transfer window.

Peace and long live torrent,



Moskollo
